name: Many Mouths
description:
So many mouths to feed - Luckily he'll eat anything!
Somethings in the water, - at least judging by the look of these creatures! Crazy Fish is a fun series of 100 "Uneek" NFTS featuring characters from under the sea which are being released Sept/Oct 2021. Each NFT of the Crazy Fish series is hand drawn, digitally coloured and is released as a single collectable NFT. Signed and individually numbered.  Ready to go fishing?
